    "The sum of infinitely many infinitesimal volumes along the infinite length of the horn is… infinite!",
    "We could argue that what is called an infinite series is often a continuous series that terminates at a convenient (for our calculation) finite point, with the understanding that adding more terms does not significantly change the practical result.",
    "Can a machine present cognition?",
    "Can it present agency without human intervention?",
    "It is possible that there cannot be a set of deterministically accurate answers to our questions in this manuscript."
